These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, ritmeester, davidoff
3 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, snake
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, crime
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold, tulip
House: townhouse, cottage, art-deco
3 different games are played: scrabble, chess, bridge
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, october, july
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is the person playing chess##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who growstulip##1
 3. the davidoff-smoker is between the person playing bridge and the ritmeester-smoker##2
 4. the cottage house is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is the owner of the snake##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
10. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Cigar      | ritmeester    | davidoff   | dannemann           |
| Pet          | guinea-pig       | snake    | horse         |
| Movie-Genre         | fantasy    | crime  | animation        |
| Flower           | poppy | marigold   | tulip      |
| House   | cottage        | art-deco    | townhouse       |
| Game   | chess     | scrabble  | bridge       |
| Birthday         | november     | october | july |

