The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, ship, tram
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, ebony, brown
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, oliveros, cain
 1. the person who likes brown is the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person who likes brown is the person playing bridge##1
 3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 4. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
 5. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is the entrepreneur##1
 7. the bartender is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person playing bridge is on the right of the social-worker##1
10. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Hobby      | cooking   | singing    | fishing         |
| Birthday          | july    | february | may          |
| Game   | monopoly  | bridge  | go     |
