3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, prince, alhambra
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, tulip, rose
 1. the alhambra-smoker is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
 3. the fan folk is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 4. the person traveling to new-york is the person who likes blood-red##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the fan folk##1
 6. the person playing go is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who growsrose is between the person who's birthday is in december and the fan jazz##2
 8. the person who likes black is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is the person who growsbellflower##1
10. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
11. the person who growsbellflower is the fan jazz##1

